OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FA mother who believed she was dying
OL,7,Fwhile giving birth says she has been
OL,8,Fleft so traumatised it has made her
OL,9,Fnever want children again.
OL,11,FJess Jones, 31, says she had always
OL,12,Fplanned on having two or three
OL,13,Fchildren, but after undergoing a
OL,14,Fterrifying pregnancy she faced an
OL,15,Femergency C-section to bring her son
OL,16,FCharlie into the world.
OL,18,FThe experience has left the mum so
OL,19,Ftraumatised she says her "dream" of
OL,20,Fhaving a big family has been taken
OL,21,Ffrom her.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/13
