OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,F"I feel I was failed," the mum from
OL,7,FHelsby, Cheshire, said. "My ambition
OL,8,Fwas to always have two, three
OL,9,Fchildren, that was always my dream,
OL,10,Fafter what I've been through, it's
OL,11,Ftaken that away from me."
OL,13,FJess is just one of thousands of women
OL,14,Fwho gave evidence to a parliamentary
OL,15,Finquiry which is now calling for
OL,16,Fbetter maternity services.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
