OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FThe Birth Trauma Inquiry , and said
OL,7,Fmany are often "treated as an
OL,8,Finconvenience" while poor care in
OL,9,Fmaternity units was "frequently
OL,10,Ftolerated as normal."
OL,12,FJess's issues first began when her
OL,13,Fwaters broke at just 13 weeks and
OL,14,FCharlie was given a 2% chance of
OL,15,Fsurvival.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/13
