OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FShe told medics she wanted to continue
OL,7,Fwith her pregnancy, and eight weeks
OL,8,Fbefore her due date, she had to
OL,9,Fundergo an emergency C-section to
OL,10,Fbring Charlie, now four, into the
OL,11,Fworld.
OL,13,FBut during the procedure Jess says she
OL,14,Fwas told very little, and at one point
OL,15,Fshe believed medics had showed her her
OL,16,Fson as a way of saying goodbye.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/13
