OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,F"They took Charlie away, and that's
OL,7,Fwhere my key trauma is there because
OL,8,Fin that moment I could feel them
OL,9,Ftugging, I could feel just rummaging,
OL,10,Fthat was the only way I could explain
OL,11,Fit," she said.
OL,13,F"I think I physically grabbed someone
OL,14,Fby their arm and I said, 'please tell
OL,15,Fme is this normal, because I feel like
OL,16,Fsomething is going wrong'.
OL,18,F"I said 'I could feel things too much,
OL,19,Fis this normal, am I okay, what is
OL,20,Fhappening?'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
