OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,F"It was just like I was just palmed
OL,7,Foff, it was like 'ah you're fine' and
OL,8,FI was like 'I'm not, I'm really
OL,9,Fstruggling here, I just need someone
OL,10,Fto sit with me and just explain to me
OL,11,Fwhat's happening, where's my baby and
OL,12,Fwhat's going on?'
OL,14,F"It did get to the point where they
OL,15,Fdid put me to sleep in the end because
OL,16,FI wasn't coping, I thought I was
OL,17,Fdying."
