OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FJess is one of an estimated 30,000
OL,7,Fwomen across the UK who have suffered
OL,8,Fa traumatic birth. The issue is now
OL,9,Fthe centre of a damning report.
OL,11,FThe Birth Trauma Inquiry has heard
OL,12,Fharrowing evidence from more than
OL,13,F1,300 women.
OL,15,FSome say they were left in blood-
OL,16,Fsoaked sheets while others and their
OL,17,Fchildren suffered life-changing
OL,18,Finjuries due to medical negligence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
