OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FA third of the women who gave
OL,7,Ftestimony to the inquiry said they
OL,8,Fexperienced traumatic births, while
OL,9,Fone out of 25 were left with post
OL,10,Ftraumatic stress disorder (PTSD).
OL,12,FResponding to the findings, the
OL,13,Freport's authors wrote: "In many of
OL,14,Fthese cases, the trauma was caused by
OL,15,Fmistakes and failures made before and
OL,16,Fduring labour.
OL,18,F"Frequently, these errors were covered
OL,19,Fup by hospitals who frustrated
OL,20,Fparents' efforts to find answers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
