OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,F"There were also many stories of care
OL,7,Fthat lacked compassion, including
OL,8,Fwomen not being listened to when they
OL,9,Ffelt something was wrong, being mocked
OL,10,For shouted at and being denied basic
OL,11,Fneeds such as pain relief."
OL,13,FAmong the recommendations included in
OL,14,Fthe report is the creation of a
OL,15,Fmaternity commissioner reporting to
OL,16,Fthe prime minister.
OL,18,FMaria Repanos, from Hudgell Solicitors
OL,19,Fin Manchester, says she has seen a
OL,20,Fspike in mothers turning to her for
OL,21,Fhelp.
