OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,FShe said: "We deal with those cases
OL,7,Fthat meet the cases to meet the
OL,8,Fthreshold for them to bring a claim.
OL,10,F"There might be more vulnerable
OL,11,Fmembers of society, people who are
OL,12,Fneurodiverse, those where English
OL,13,Fisn't their first language, we see
OL,14,Fsome of those individuals but I
OL,15,Fimagine there are lots we don't see."
OL,17,FYana Richens, Director of Midwifery,
OL,18,FLiverpool Women's NHS Foundation
OL,19,FTrust, where Jess had her son, said
OL,20,Fthey were looking into her case.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/13
