OL,3,CMum traumatised by birth says she will
OL,4,Cnever have children again
OL,6,F"Good communication is key to
OL,7,Fproviding a positive experience and we
OL,8,Fare sorry that we have not met the
OL,9,Fhigh standards we expect on this
OL,10,Foccasion," she said.
OL,12,F"We are looking into this to
OL,13,Funderstand what we could have done
OL,14,Fbetter. As a Trust we always aim to
OL,15,Frespond to individual feedback from
OL,16,Fwomen and families proactively, to
OL,17,Faddress concerns raised and to make
OL,18,Fimprovements where required.
