OL,6,F"We are also currently in the process
OL,7,Fof reviewing the Birth Trauma Inquiry
OL,8,Freport to understand what we can learn
OL,9,Fas a Trust to make improvements within
OL,10,Four services, based on the
OL,11,Frecommendations within the report. We
OL,12,Fwill work with the wider NHS and our
OL,13,Fservice users to do this.
OL,15,F"We will continue to listen to and
OL,16,Fsupport women in our care who
OL,17,Fexperience a traumatic birth, to
OL,18,Fensure that they are given timely
OL,19,Faccess to ongoing support."
